  "body": "### Description of the Feature\r\n\r\nAs part of the on-going work in https://github.com/MyCryptoHQ/MyCrypto/issues/774, @wbobeirne has mocked up a TX history component that will show progress as confirmations are broadcast during `sweeper` sweeps.\r\n\r\nThis TX history component should be generic enough to also apply to our Send view, so that we can display the transaction history for the unlocked account.\r\n\r\n### Example(s) of Feature\r\n\r\nCurrently, we link out to [etherscan](https://etherscan.io/address/0xcfceab0b7380befc8952a674df2fcff0398bd2a7) so that users can view their transaction history.",
